# Fuel Core

Full formulas, gravity values, reverse processing, and acceptance tests → [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).

## When editing this package

- Pure functions only — no I/O, WebSocket, or React
- Use `FUEL_FORMULA` map for launch/land coefficients (do not inline ternaries)
- Use `GRAVITY` from `@nasa-fuel/shared`
- Explicit return types on exported functions
